          Product description

          Tata Salt Rock Salt is sourced directly from mountains and hence it is intact with natural minerals such as calcium, magnesium and potassium. This salt adds a fresh flavour burst to your everyday meals, meals for special occasions and can also be used to enhance fasting foods. The zip lock packaging of sendhanamak salt keeps its freshness intact for longer. Now indulge in your favourite dishes with fresh flavours and natural minerals of Tata Rock Salt.
